headline: Raymond James Welcomes Virginia Advisor Managing Over $280 Million
summary: ST. PETERSBURG, Fla., October 30, 2025--Raymond James (NYSE: RJF) recently welcomed financial advisor J. Morgan Edwards to Raymond James & Associates – the firm’s employee advisor channel.
